The long green tail of =E2=80=98Wicked=E2=80=99/=E2=80=98Moana 2=E2=80=99 h=
elped break more box office records this weekend, proving that the public w=
as still primed and ready to fill seats the week after Thanksgiving. Too ba=
d the studios lack the courage to give them something big to see.

SCOTT MENDELSON ( https://puck.news/author/scott-mendelson/?utm_campaign=3D=
What+I%27m+Hearing+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2812%2F9%2F24%29&utm_content=3DWhat+I%27m=
