=E2=80=99s <i>Y2K</i>) and sizes (Sony and Crunchyroll=E2=80=99s <i>Solo Le=
veling: ReAwakening</i>) combined to earn another $19 million, with $4.8 mi=
llion coming from Tollywood=E2=80=99s <i>Pushpa 2: The Rule </i>and $4.6 mi=
