 missed opportunity to have programmed a more ambitious film to take advant=
age of the lingering theatrical appetite.   <br/><br/>In the old days, back=
 when films were cheaper, legs were longer, and a larger variety of non-I.P=
=2E genres were commercially viable, Ho=
llywood treated the post-Thanksgiving=20=
